Both the prototype and the body are needed to determine if const qualification is possible.

To determine whether OS_CondVarSignal_Impl must modify the token (and thus whether its parameter must be non-const), we need to see how this downstream function uses the token (its prototype and implementation), since that usage propagates const-ness requirements.
